title: Danny & Dr. Wendy Osefo (The Real Housewives of Potomac)
itunes:title: Danny & Dr. Wendy Osefo (The Real Housewives of Potomac)
description:
Danny catches up with Dr. Wendy Osefo, cast member on The Real Housewives of Potomac and author of the new book, Tears of My Mother! Dr. Wendy shares more about her upbringing, relationship with her mother, what's to come on the upcoming season of Potomac, and what didn't air at the reunion!
